How to setup react application css in javascript.

You need to run this command from your application root directory 


npm run eject

then it will generate script and config folder in your application go to config folder and open dev file 
find this function use: getStyleLoaders(


 use: getStyleLoaders({
              importLoaders: 1,
              modules: true,
              localIdentName: '[name]__[local]__[hash:base64:5]'
            }),
            
